---
// src/components/Footer.astro

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white pt-24 pb-12 relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
  
  <!-- Decorative Background Glow -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-5 mix-blend-soft-light pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-[#0EA5E9]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-[#0D9488]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 relative z-10">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-8 mb-20">
      
      <!-- Brand Section -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="group flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
           <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#0EA5E9] to-[#0D9488] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-md shadow-[#0EA5E9]/15 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg>
           </div>
           <div>
              <span class="block text-xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Amtly</span>
              <span class="block text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#0EA5E9] font-black">Staatliche Zuschüsse</span>
           </div>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 max-w-sm font-light mb-8">
          Wir demokratisieren den Zugang zu sozialen Rechten durch moderne Technologie. Unabhängig, 100% anonym, sicher und digital.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation Column 1: Services -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0D9488]">
          Services
        </span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/#calculator" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Universal-Fördercheck</a>
          <a href="#" onclick="if (window.openLeadModal) { window.openLeadModal('legal_help'); } else { window.location.href = '/?action=legal_help'; } return false;" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Bescheid-Prüfung</a>
          <a href="/lexikon/" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Rechts-Lexikon</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation Column 2: Company -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0D9488]">
          Unternehmen
        </span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/ueber-uns/" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Über uns</a>
          <a href="/agb/" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">AGB</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation Column 3: Legal -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0D9488]">
          Rechtliches
        </span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="/impressum/" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Impressum</a>
          <a href="/datenschutz/" class="text-sm text-slate-600 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors">Datenschutz</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">
          &copy; {currentYear} Amtly. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          Hinweis: Amtly bietet eine automatisierte, unverbindliche Ersteinschätzung auf Basis offizieller Berechnungsgrundlagen. Unsere Auswertungen dienen der Information und stellen keine Rechtsberatung im Sinne des Rechtsdienstleistungsgesetzes (RDG) dar.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
